---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aboutImage from '../assets/img/about.webp';
import logoImage from '../assets/img/bengal-logo-web.webp';
---

<section id="about" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-cream px-6 py-10 sm:px-10 sm:py-16 lg:px-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">

    <header class="mb-8 text-center sm:mb-10">
      <p class="font-body text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[2.8px] text-dark/45 sm:text-[0.72rem] lg:text-[0.76rem]">
        Our Story
      </p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-heading text-[1.5rem] font-light leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-gold-dark sm:text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.2rem] xl:text-[2.4rem]">
        About <span class="italic">Luxury Rosettes</span>
      </h2>
      <span class="mx-auto mt-4 block h-px w-16 bg-(--gold-line) sm:w-20"></span>
    </header>

    <figure class="relative mb-8 overflow-hidden rounded-md sm:mb-10">
      <Image
        src={aboutImage}
        alt="Luxury Rosettes founder with Bengal cat and awards"
        class="h-65 w-full object-cover object-center sm:h-85 lg:h-105"
        widths={[480, 640, 768]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px"
        loading="lazy"
        format="webp"
        quality={78}
      />
    </figure>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[66ch] text-center font-body text-[0.9rem] font-normal leading-[1.85] text-dark/80 sm:text-[0.95rem] lg:leading-[1.9]">
      <p>
        Our journey with Bengal cats began 15 years ago with a gift from my husband. What started as one special moment became a lifelong passion. Their wild elegance and affectionate character quickly made them part of our family.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-5 sm:mt-6">
        At Luxury Rosettes, we do not just breed Bengals. We live with them, love them, and admire them every day. Their intelligence, playful spirit, and breathtaking rosettes make them inseparable from our home.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center sm:mt-10">
      <Image
        src={logoImage}
        alt="Luxury Rosettes Bengal Cattery"
        class="h-auto w-45 opacity-80 sm:w-52.5 lg:w-60"
        loading="lazy"
        widths={[180, 210, 240, 320]}
        sizes="240px"
        format="webp"
      />
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
